title: Nature vs Humanity
subhtml:
Nature vs Humanity

Painted for Dublin Body Painting competition 2018. 2nd place in Freestyle category. The theme was "Untold Stories". I wanted to represent the untold story of that which has no voice, nature and its strugles against humanity.

title: Shaman
subhtml:
Shaman

Painted during the Dublin Tattoo Expo 2016 the theme for which was 'tribal'. My interpretation involves a shaman from a tribe that worships dragons with dragon wings along the chest and a dragon skull.

title: Greed
subhtml:
Greed

This body painting was inspired by Greed. Two jewel encursted snakes fighting over a mound of gold. Respresenting the rich getting richer, but in the end we all die and it means nothing.

title: Uv Mythology

Uv Mythology
